College Domain – Student Performance Prediction

Problem: Predict whether a student will pass or fail.

Input → Output:

Input: Attendance %, Previous Marks, Study Hours, Assignment Scores

Output: Pass / Fail (Classification)

College Domain – Placement Prediction

Problem: Predict whether a student will get placed in campus recruitment.

Input → Output:

Input: CGPA, Internship Experience, Technical Skills Score, Aptitude Test Score

Output: Placed / Not Placed (Classification)

Healthcare Domain – Disease Prediction

Problem: Predict whether a patient has a particular disease (e.g., diabetes).

Input → Output:

Input: Age, BMI, Blood Pressure, Glucose Level, Family History

Output: Disease Present / Not Present (Classification)

Healthcare Domain – Hospital Readmission Prediction

Problem: Predict if a patient will be readmitted within 30 days.

Input → Output:

Input: Diagnosis Type, Length of Stay, Previous Admissions, Age

Output: Readmitted / Not Readmitted (Classification)

Shopping Domain – Product Recommendation System

Problem: Recommend products to customers based on their behavior.

Input → Output:

Input: Browsing History, Purchase History, Cart Items, Search Queries

Output: Recommended Products (Recommendation System)

Shopping Domain – Price Prediction

Problem: Predict the price of a product.

Input → Output:

Input: Brand, Features, Ratings, Demand Level

Output: Predicted Price (Regression)